BUSINESS SOLUTIONS.

MICROSOFT BUSINESS SOLUTIONS CONTINUES TO EXPAND ITS SMALL AND MID-MARKET OFFERINGS WITH KEY INVESTMENTS IN TECHNOLOGIES FOR CRM, ONLINE

