HUMAN RESOURCES, LEGAL, FINANCE, IT, CORPORATE DEVELOPMENT AND PROCUREMENT ACTIVITIES, RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT AND OTHER COSTS, AND ACCRUED LEGAL CONTINGENCIES. CORPORATE EXPENSES WERE $3.08 BILLION, $3.74 BILLION AND $4.66 BILLION IN FISCAL 2002,

