IN JULY 2004, THE FASB RATIFIED EMERGING ISSUES TASK FORCE (EITF) CONSENSUS ON ISSUE NO. 02-14,

WHETHER AN INVESTOR SHOULD APPLY THE EQUITY METHOD OF ACCOUNTING

